  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK433">
<l>tiṉaittuṇaiyāṅ kuṟṟam variṉum paṉaittuṇaiyāk</l>
<l>koḷvar paḻināṇu vār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who fear guilt, if they commit a fault small as a millet seed, will consider it to be as large as a palmyra tree.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
